inst the baseline from 20:29 UTC, the pipeline is stable—no new sessions have spawned, no existing ones have died, and there are no failures or blockers to report. Everything appears to be running as expected, so there's nothing that needs to be flagged.","thinkingSignature":"319c9b9829afa23537c0dcca916316085a2714e3211bdba0049b75800dda6cdf"},{"type":"text","text":"Silent. No state changes since last baseline (20:29 UTC).\n\n**Current stable sessions confirmed:**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running (~35 min, updated 21:01 UTC)\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ running (updated 20:56 UTC)\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ running (updated 20:03 UTC — stale but alive)\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ running (updated 20:29 UTC)\n\nPipeline: HEALTHY. Blockers: none."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":20128,"output":693,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":416,"totalTokens":35181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776200545927,"responseId":"062dde63a0568fa0da6d268700037b24"}}
